    <h2>Quality Assurance </h2>
    <p>Our Quality Assurance Committee ensures that the university maintains strong teaching and learning standards. It also approves curriculum, leads accreditation processes, and among others, has advisory responsibility for academic facilities on campus. </p>
    <a href="https://www.ashesi.edu.gh/images/academics/docs/Final_Quality_Assurance_Manual2016_2017_B.pdf">Read our Manual </a>
